`ftd_django` is a Python package that lets you use [`ftd`](https://ftd.dev) and
[`fpm`](https://fpm.dev) with your [Django
project](https://www.djangoproject.com).

Primary way to use `ftd` files with Django via the
[`ftd_django.TemplateBackend`](django/template-backend/).

